Class TabControl.Tabbable.Tab

    TabControl.Tabbable

    public static class TabControl.Tabbable.Tab
extends java.lang.Object
    This class wraps a TabControl's Tab object.
    For now, the embedded Tab object can be a Map.

    APR 21, 2014 (Lei Wang) Initial release.
